Package: littag
Title: Lit-tag: an app for custom annotation of a citation database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul", "McElhany", , "paul.mcelhany@noaa.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Starting with a citation library exported from Zotero, the lit-tag builder interface allows the creation custom annotation tags and notes. The lit-tag view module provides options to search the annotated database, generate custom reports, create summary graphics.
